      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 111,
      "message": "Yes it should be feasible but I don't like it so much:\n* This maven configuration is very specific to this RestControlLoopManagerTest class. Changing the surefire plugin configuration would be done in feature-control-loop-management/pom.xml, I presume. Then it would affect all the build process for this module. For now I would not give it higher visibility than the class it belongs to. \n* I also prefer keeping this maven config very localized and hidden to this test class as I don't recommend building much more test cases having a bulky dependency on nexus to run.\n* Moving the default values from the test class to pom.xml would require to provide it manually when running unit tests from ide tool without maven.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5658,
        "name": "Bruno Sakoto",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "bruno.sakoto@bell.ca",
